channel.title: Help would be appreciated, "your account is already logged in"
channel.description:
Okay, before anyone says that I need a different source or something of the sort, I am not trying to log into someone elses server, just the moparscape client itself.
I had successfully done it on the webclient and the downloadable one a few days ago but it seems whatever password/username that I use it says "your account is already logged in"
If anyone has an explanation please state it along with a detailed way on how to fix it.
Would be very appreciative :D
